{"tid":1313760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大件事冇人講，美國正苦部門比難民示威者攻佔，升起墨西哥國旗","createTime":"2019-07-14T01:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:21:49.000Z","uid":130105,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d83b75216abbedb250ba091886677e9b1519a89","tid":1313760,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"噚晚睇見笑咗出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n========================<br />\n&bull;Chief Nick Metz described in a tweet that the majority of the protesters at the Aurora ICE Processing Center were 'peaceful', even thanking officers<br />\n&bull;But a separate group was said to have split from the majority, storming the barriers and pulling down the Colorado State Flag and the United States flag<br />\n&bull;They then hoisted a Mexican flag in place of the state's flag while also putting up a defaced 'Blue Lives Matter' flag in place of the American flag<br />\n&bull;Officers later took down the flags and were seen hoisting Old Glory back up <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/07/13/16/16003466-7243975-image-a-24_1563032989154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F07%2F13%2F16%2F16003466-7243975-image-a-24_1563032989154.jpg&h=88416531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Chief Nick Metz described in a tweet that the majority of the protesters at the Aurora ICE Processing Center were 'peaceful', even thanking officers<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/07/13/16/16003442-7243975-image-a-22_1563032968399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F07%2F13%2F16%2F16003442-7243975-image-a-22_1563032968399.jpg&h=2475440c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n But a separate group was said to have split from the majority, storming the barriers and pulling down the Colorado State Flag and the United States flag<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/07/13/16/16003400-7243975-image-m-25_1563033003528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F07%2F13%2F16%2F16003400-7243975-image-m-25_1563033003528.jpg&h=e156ba46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n They then hoisted a Mexican flag in place of the state's flag while also putting up a deface 'Blue Lives Matter' flag in place of the American flag.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/07/13/16/16003392-7243975-image-a-26_1563033015683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F07%2F13%2F16%2F16003392-7243975-image-a-26_1563033015683.jpg&h=f20d3457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The protest was part of the #LightsForLiberty events that took place across the country, and was called the 'March to Close Concentration Camps' on Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/07/13/2092663879732382974/1024x576_MP4_2092663879732382974.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F07%2F13%2F2092663879732382974%2F1024x576_MP4_2092663879732382974.mp4&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=78eef6e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/07/13/2092663879732382974/1024x576_MP4_2092663879732382974.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7243975/Anti-ICE-protesters-flag-Colorado-migrant-holding-facility.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-7243975%2FAnti-ICE-protesters-flag-Colorado-migrant-holding-facility.html&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=56c89364\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailyma